{
  "texts": [
    "Ma et al. (2018) applied NIR-HSI to assess the soluble solids content (SSC) of apples.",
    "The relationship between SSC reference data and NIR spectral data taken from each sample was determined using PLS regression analysis.",
    "HSI can also be used to determine polyphenol oxidase (PPO) activity, which is important for controlling the quality of the finished product.",
    "For indirect measurement of PPO activity in fresh-cut apple slices, Shrestha et al. (2020) employed the VIS-NIR.",
    "The authors found that HSI could be used as an alternative for conventional chemical evaluation of PPO enzyme activity."
  ]
}